 (THE SPLITTER) found no merged words in this batch. \n\nPROTOCOL 2 (THE JUDGE) and PROTOCOL 7 (THE FILTER) led to the discarding of two entries: 'ከቆ' was discarded because 'ቆ' is a single character and thus too short to be a meaningful Amharic word or root on its own. 'ከቆች' was discarded as 'ቆች' is semantically meaningless and could not be reliably corrected to a known Amharic word without speculative guessing. \n\nPROTOCOL 3 (THE CORRECTOR) was applied to 'ከቅዴሞትም'. The 'ዴ' was corrected to 'ድ' to form 'ቅድሞት' (precedence, priority), a minor and certain OCR correction. Punctuation was not present in the input. \n\nPROTOCOL 4 (THE LEMMATIZER) focused on identifying the global citation form. For verbs like 'ቆረጠላቸው', the infinitive 'መቁረጥ' was identified as the root. For nouns and adjectives, the base form (e.g., 'ቅምጥልነት' from 'ቅምጥልነትዋ', 'ቅዱስነት' from 'ቅዱስነትህና') was used as the root. Words like 'ቄኔዛዊ', 'ቅማንት', 'ቅትር', 'ቋንቋ', 'ቋፍ', 'ቈላ', 'ቈንጆ', 'ቊስል', 'ቍርስራሽ', and 'ቍርባን' were considered their own roots as they are base nouns or adjectives. 'ቋሚ' was treated as a noun in its context ('the permanent ones').\n\nPROTOCOL 6 (THE GRAMMARIAN) assigned high-level parts of speech. Words like 'ቅድሞ' were correctly identified as Adverbs, while others functioned as Nouns or Verbs based on their morphology and typical usage. Importance scores were assigned based on general frequency and significance in Amharic vocabulary.","input_words":["ከቄኔዛዊው","ከቅማንትም","ከቅምጥልነት","ከቅምጥልነትዋ","ከቅብዓቱ","ከቅብዓቱም","ከቅትር","ከቅንአትና","ከቅዱስነትህና","ከቅዴሞትም","ከቅድሞ","ከቅጠልም","ከቅጠሎችና","ከቅጥራችን","ከቆ","ከቆረጠላቸው","ከቆሮንቶስ","ከቆሰለ","ከቆች","ከቈለፈ","ከቈላውም","ከቈንጆ","ከቈጠረ","ከቊስላችሁም","ከቋሚዎቹ","ከቋንቋዎችም","ከቋፍ","ከቍርስራሹም","ከቍርባኑም","ከቍርባናችሁም"],"batch_number":null,"batch_label":null,"model_version":"gemini-2.5-flash"},{"id":"0917c75c-3ccc-4c4f-b446-cde576a3eabb","created_at":"2026-03-04T08:19:15.277423+00:00","word":null,"source_file":"rare_words_24/chunk_0666.txt","batch_index":0,"words":[{"pos":"Noun","root":"ፌስቡክ","word":"ፌስቡክ","synonyms":[